name: NSPositionalSpecifier.InsertionPosition
desc: The following constants are defined by NSPositionalSpecifier to specify an insertion position.

items.name: case after
items.desc: Specifies a position after another object.

items.name: case before
items.desc: Specifies a position before another object.

items.name: case beginning
items.desc: Specifies a position at the beginning of a collection.

items.name: case end
items.desc: Specifies a position at the end of a collection.

items.name: case replace
items.desc: Specifies a position in the place of another object.
